  "response_text": "Against a clean white background, a small gold Dove bird logo appears above centered grey text that reads, “Did you know that Dove Bar washes away germs?” The scene then changes to a simple demonstration: a white plate with a dark navy rim sits on a white surface, and the pale center of the plate is scattered with many tiny black specks. Using the transcript for context, these specks are presented as pepper standing in for germs.\n\nA hand enters over a shallow glass dish holding a white Dove Beauty Bar. The bar is wet and surrounded by a little water. The hand holds a dark blue, dove-shaped applicator or scraper and rubs it across the top of the curved white bar. At the bottom of the image, grey text reads, “With Dove…” The hand continues sliding the blue shape back and forth over the soap, pressing lightly across its smooth surface.\n\nThe demonstration returns to the plate with the black specks. The blue dove-shaped tool moves quickly across the top edge of the plate, and grey text below reads, “the germs wash away.” The image suggests the specks are being cleared as part of the washing demonstration. Next, on another white background, a thin stream of white cream pours downward into a small mound, with grey text underneath: “Made with ¼ moisturizing cream.”\n\nThe commercial then moves into a real bathroom setting. At a sink with a chrome faucet and pale countertop, a person wearing a light blue robe holds a white cleansing bar under running water. Only the torso and hands are visible at first. The hands turn and rub the bar together near the basin, lathering and rinsing as water flows from the faucet on the left.\n\nA fair-skinned adult woman with red hair tied up in a bun appears at the bathroom mirror. She wears the same light blue robe. Leaning slightly forward, she gently touches her chin and jawline with her fingertips, looking at her reflection with a soft, satisfied expression. Her skin is clean and bare, and she slowly moves her hand along her chin as if checking how her face feels after washing.\n\nThe final image returns to a bright white product display. A white Dove Beauty Bar with the embossed Dove bird rests above a white Dove package. The package shows the Dove name in dark lettering with the gold bird logo beneath it. To the right, large grey text reads, “Cleans Effectively. Cares Beautifully.” Below the text is a gold circular seal highlighting the “¼” moisturizing cream message.",
